<br>
I think as the internet grows, we must begin to consider it in equal light to our life experiences.  The people I speak to online are just as real, and just as important as those I meet face to face.  The difference between face to face communication and text communication is meaningless. Both mediums do the same thing. <br>
<br>
Consider the way a blind person experiences the world. Does his lack of sight mean his relationships and experiences are something less than a sighted persons experiences?  <br>
<br>
I prefer the online world to the real world. It's happier here, and I am free to be myself in every single way possible, without having to constantly second guess myself. I have little care for what others think of me, but it's impossible to ever really be yourself when you are around other people, even when the comfort level is very high. <p><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-family:perpetua;font-size:x-small;"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=421973">Turzem Setanta</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->--<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower">Arch Mage</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=zyrexxshadowfyre@themagicianstower>Zyrexx Shadowfyre</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master Summoner</span><br>  Posts: 485<br> <font color=#333333>(11/12/02 3:32:11 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7809.topic&index=46>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: .</span><hr size=1> Thats one of the problems with the net, most people have no fear of reprisal for being a jackass. All those halfwits that are jerks just to be jerks would not dare do that with you in real life as you would hand them their ass.<br>
